I've added a [PKGBUILD for
pepper](http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=45324) to the [Arch User
Repository](http://aur.archlinux.org/). Arch users can install the program
now using their favorite AUR package manager, e.g. `yaourt -S scm-pepper`.

In order to add support for all available repository types, the
`subversion` and `mercurial` packages should be installed first.
